    {
      "instruction": "<p>Set aside a few<strong> basil leaves </strong>and <strong>mint leaves</strong> and <strong>half </strong>of your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>for garnish</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
