        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>fresh tagliatelle </strong>and <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the tagliatelle is cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> tagliatelle & peas</strong>, reserve the pot and a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
