        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pasta is cooking, add the <strong>peeled garlic</strong>,<strong> pistachio nuts</strong>, <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong>, <strong>remaining basil</strong>, including the stalks, and<strong> remaining mint leaves </strong>to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Tip: No food processor? Chop everything up as finely as you can and mix it together!</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong>, 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
