      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat and add the<strong> drained tagliatelle</strong> <strong>& peas</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>pistachio pesto</strong> and stir gently until the pasta is coated in the pesto and everything is warmed through</p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
